Dummy module to show how to write your own extension or override some files.

classes - if you want to override kernel classe create a file in classes folder and define it's path in var/autoloads/lhextension_autoload.php file

design - here you can overide default templates

modules - contains example how to write your own module or override default modules files.

To active module

Adjust settings to the following

'extensions' => 
      array (
        0 => 'customstatus',
),